<h3>About Margaret</h3>

<p>Margaret's life journey has taken her from the east coast to the west, and from teaching to coding. Her life has a great soundtrack and she's happy as long as she's learning.</p>

<h3>Margaret's Skills</h3>
<p>Click a skill to see examples and endorsements of that skill.</p>
<% @skills.each do |skill| %>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col sm-4">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-block">
        <h3><%= link_to skill.description, skill_path(skill) %></h3>
        <% if current_user && current_user.admin %>
          <%= link_to 'Edit skill', edit_skill_path(skill) %>
          <%= link_to 'Delete skill', edit_skill_path(skill) %>
        <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div><br>
<% end %>

<% if current_user && current_user.admin %>
  <%= link_to 'Add a skill', new_skill_path %>
<% end %>
